reviewText: nice films, some better than others.
I liked all the movies on this one. They are great stories and I have read the books to some of them.
Most of the movies were enjoyable. Hard To Forget and A Change of Place were my least favorite.
Good romantic drama with good plots and such...
Stories were okay. Nudity not neceessary.
The movies were good. Just in some did not expect full nudity. Really was not necessary.
